extends layout

block content
  section.hero
    div.container
      h1 Small-batch gin, wild New Zealand soul.
      p.lead Crafted in micro batches in Mangaroa, Upper Hutt using botanicals foraged from native bush and coastal gardens.
      a.button.button-primary(href="#contact") Book a tasting
      a.button.button-secondary(href="#range") Explore the range
  section.section#story
    div.container
      h2 Our story
      p
        | Longstream Botanicals began as a kitchen-bench experiment between friends chasing the perfect evening tipple. What
        | started with recycled jars and an old copper still has grown into a community of home distillers, foragers, and
        | flavour seekers. Every bottle captures the terroir of its season, balancing bright coastal citrus with wild herbs
        | and the spice of native ngahere.
      p
        | We partner with local growers, harvest respectfully, and distil slowly to preserve the stories of each botanical.
  section.section#range
    div.container
      h2 Signature range
      p Discover our current line-up of homebrew favourites available for refill by appointment.
      div.card-grid
        each gin in ginRanges
          article.card
            h3= gin.name
            p= gin.description
            h4 Botanicals
            ul
              each botanical in gin.botanicals
                li= botanical
  section.section.highlight
    div.container
      h2 How we craft
      div.process-grid
        article
          h3 Harvest
          p We handpick botanicals at first light to capture maximum aroma, working closely with iwi guardians and growers.
        article
          h3 Infuse
          p Neutral spirit rests on botanicals for up to 48 hours before slow distillation in our customised pot still.
        article
          h3 Rest
          p Each batch is rested with mānuka honey and mountain water for a silky texture and bright, lingering finish.
  section.section#experiences
    div.container
      h2 Experiences & workshops
      p Join us for immersive sessions that celebrate experimentation and the joy of sharing a good drink.
      div.card-grid
        each experience in experiences
          article.card
            h3= experience.title
            p= experience.description
  section.section
    div.container
      h2 Recognition
      ul.awards-list
        each award in awards
          li
            span.year= award.year
            span.name= award.name
  section.section.cta#contact
    div.container
      h2 Visit the distillery
      p Arrange a refill, private event, or collaborative experiment. We love welcoming fellow makers.
      div.contact-card
        p
          strong Cellar door:
          |  Mangaroa, Upper Hutt, New Zealand
        p
          strong Email:
          a(href="mailto:hello@aotearoabotanicals.nz") hello@aotearoabotanicals.nz
        p
          strong Instagram:
          a(href="https://instagram.com/aotearoa.botanicals", target="_blank", rel="noopener") @aotearoa.botanicals
      a.button.button-primary(href="mailto:hello@aotearoabotanicals.nz") Start a conversation
